OL,9,G1900 GPs: Behind Closed Doors
OL,10,     FIn Birmingham, Barry worries the
OL,11,     Fcondition affecting his hands will
OL,12,     Fstop him doing the activities he
OL,13,     Floves, and Dr Abdul-Razaak lends
OL,14,     Fan ear to David who is suffering
OL,15,     Ffrom depression.
