OL,5,G2100 999: Killer On The Line
OL,6,     FThe story of how killer Brian Cox
OL,7,     Ffatally attacked father-of-five
OL,8,     FMark Webb before cleaning up the
OL,9,     Fscene and lying about what had
OL,10,     Fhappened.
OL,11,G2200 999: Critical Condition
OL,12,     FA man faces life-changing injuries
OL,13,     Fafter a firework explodes in his
OL,14,     Fhand, and a patient is treated for
OL,15,     Fsevere facial burns following an
OL,16,     Faccident with a gas canister at
OL,17,     Fhis workplace.
